Package fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.http

Services for handling HTTP communications, including management of the embedded web server.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAddress
    Represents the parsed path of a IHttpServiceCall.
    IAddressableService
    Handles HTTP requests mapped to an address space.
    IContentType
    Represents a HTTP content type, based on a media type with an optional charset.
    ICookie
    HTTP header cookie representation.
    IFilteringService
    Filters HTTP requests mapped to an address space.
    IFormConstraints
    Provides access to constraints for processing multipart HTTP content, such as file uploads.
    IFormPart
    Represents an item in a multipart form, such as fields and file uploads.
    IHttpAttributes
    Provides access to session and call (request) attributes for an HTTP call.
    IHttpEndPoint
    Provides base location information for incoming HTTP connections and upstream HTTP connections.
    IHttpService
    Provides high-level access to the embedded HTTP server.
    IHttpServiceCall
    Incoming HTTP request/response.
    IQValue
    HTTP header "q-value" representation.
    IRequestHeaders
    Provides access to HTTP request headers.
    IResponseHeaders
    Provides access to HTTP response headers.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DispositionType
    Represents a standard disposition type for HTTP response content.
